import React from "react";
import { Box, FormControl, InputLabel, Input, FormHelperText, TextField } from '@mui/material';

const ContactForm = () => {
    return(
        <Box sx={{ width: 500, maxWidth: '100%' }}>
        <FormControl >
            <TextField id="firstName" label="Filled" variant="filled" fullWidth />
            <TextField id="lastName" label="Filled" variant="filled" fullWidth />
        </FormControl>
        <FormControl>
            <InputLabel htmlFor="my-input">Email address</InputLabel>
            <Input id="my-input" aria-describedby="my-helper-text" fullWidth />
            <FormHelperText id="my-helper-text">example@example.com</FormHelperText>
        </FormControl>
        <FormControl>
            <TextField
            id="filled-textarea"
            label="Message"
            placeholder="message"
            multiline
            variant="filled"
            fullWidth
            />
        </FormControl>
        </Box>
    );
}

export default ContactForm;
